default. 
defaultMore countries are becoming less reliant on aid and the kind of aid support they need is evolving, so it is basically a good thing if they are building more of their capacity, as you say, and can raise more of their own tax revenue
default. 
defaultThat is an absolutely fundamental thing
default. 
defaultCountries do not really want to be dependent and we do not want them to be dependent either
default. 
defaultThose two things going together, as often as not, are success measures.
