defaultQ16default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultPauline Latham:default At what point do you check that
default? 
defaultThey can say in their budget they are going to spend something; we can then put money in; but in year they can take it out
default. 
defaultDo you track what they do in year
default? 
defaultMark defaultLowcockdefault: Yes, absolutely
default. 
defaultOf course, the credibility of what they say they are going to do the following year is heavily informed by what they actually did the previous year and what they told us about that
default. 
defaultThis is something that, under the framework normally provided by the IMF and the World Bank, our economists in every cou
defaultntry 
defaultare
default very heavily engaged with. 
defaultIt is an absolutely core part of what we talk to 
defaultGovernment
defaults about and what we track.
defaultJoy defaultHutcheondefault: Every budget support programme has a performance framework where results that are going to be achieved through the additional funding are set out, and there is a process every year of scrutinising the new budget and having a discussion with the 
defaultGovernment
default about budget allocations
default. 
defaultThe third thing that is worth mentioning is that we always, in budget support countries, work on strengthening public financial management systems very closely and support the national audit system, so that we are growing the capacity of the auditor general and the country’s own ability to audit its finances
default. 
defaultA number of the crises that we have had have been uncovered by the country’s own audit systems, national audit office and public accounts committees.
default&#xa0;
defaultQ17default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultPauline Latham:default Who discovered the crisis in 
defaultUganda
default?
defaultMark defaultLowcockdefault: It was exactly that set of institutions
default. 
defaultI am trying not to use the word “schizophrenic”
default, but 
defaultwe are a teeny bit schizophrenic about what happened in 
