defaultRichard Calvertdefault: Just a couple of very brief points: one of the keys to the change in the business case is actually splitting what was previously the business case into two documents
default. 
defaultWe have what is essentially an appraisal and approval document on the one hand and, on the other hand, a programme delivery plan
